<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-05 13:34 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> The Top Fives in TV, Movies, Music  </HEADLINE>
By The Associated Press	   
TELEVISION
<TEXT>
<P>
   1. ''Who Wants to be a Millionaire-Tuesday,'' ABC.
</P>
<P>
   2. ''Who Wants to be a Millionaire-Thursday,'' ABC.
</P>
<P>
   3. ''Who Wants to be a Millionaire-Sunday,'' ABC.
</P>
<P>
   4. ''The Practice,'' ABC.
</P>
<P>
   5. ''60 Minutes,'' CBS.
</P>
<P>
