   April 10: Actor Omar Sharif is 68. Reggae artist Bunny Wailer is
53. Actor Steven Seagal is 49. Singer Terre Roche of the Roches is
47. Actor Peter MacNicol (''Ally McBeal'') is 46. Singer-producer
Kenneth ''Babyface'' Edmonds is 42. Singer Brian Setzer is 41.
Rapper Afrika Bambaataa is 40. Actor Haley Joel Osment is 12.
