   April 11: Actor Joel Grey is 68. Actor Peter Riegart is 53.
Actor Bill Irwin is 50. Musician Nigel Pulsford of Bush is 35.
Singer Lisa Stansfield is 34. Musician Dylan Keefe of Marcy
Playground is 30.
</P>
