Advanced Micro Devices Inc., up 6 11/16 at 67 13/16
</P>
<P>
   The company said it expects first-quarter sales of more than
$1.06 billion, about 10 percent higher than sales in the fourth
quarter. The semiconductor company attributed the gains to strong
sales across all product groups.
</P>
